parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the frame rail mounting bolts can cause the frame rail to drop, leading to poor steering control, loss of vehicle control, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The frame rail drops
poor steering control
loss of vehicle control
difficulty controlling the steering wheel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sliding door handles can cause the doors to become stuck or fall off, making it difficult or impossible to enter or exit the vehicle.
symptoms: Sliding door handles break off
doors become stuck or fall off
difficulty opening or closing doors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling of the paint can lead to cosmetic issues and potentially expose the underlying metal to corrosion.
symptoms: Paint peeling off the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to enter or exit the vehicle, which can lead to inconvenience, safety risks, and potential emergencies.
symptoms: The doors will not open from the outside or inside
the door handles will pull up but the lock will not disengage
the key will not unlock the doors
the doors will not open even when unlocked
intermittent problems with door opening.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected lockup of the rear brakes can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, especially on wet roads.
symptoms: The rear wheel locks up when brakes are applied
the brake pedal locks up and does not engage the brakes
the steering wheel locks up simultaneously
the vehicle does not stop properly
corrosion on the rear disc brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Front Brake Failure and Rotor Wear
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front brakes can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, especially at low speeds.
symptoms: Excessive heat buildup on the front brakes
rotor wear
brake failure due to stress created by the release of the front brake hose bracket
loss of control or accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to not properly restrain the occupant in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The seat belt will not retract
the seat belt comes out and will not retract
the seat belt retractor stopped working
the seat belt will not hold the occupant
loss of protection in the event of a crash.
